==== Members ====
The ESNM currently consists of more than 3,100 individual members and 16 affiliated societies<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.esnm.eu/affiliated-societies/|title=Affiliated Societies|work=European Society of Neurogastroenterology and Motility}}</ref> and the Gut Microbiota & Health section.

