These national and interest groups are:<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.buschkampdv.de/neurogastroenterology.eu/download/Newsletter_NO_1.pdf|title=Societies under the Umbrella of the ESNM|work=Neurogastro News|date=March 2007}}</ref> 
* Belgian Network on Gastrointestinal Regulatory Mechanisms<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.girem.be/test/links.php|title=Societies|work=Belgian Network on Gastrointestinal Regulatory mechanisms|year=2009}}</ref> (GIREM)
